                        <summary>
                            <p>Dedication of the Atiraṇacaṇdeśvara cave-temple engraved in Grantha alphabet on the right wall (north) before the entrance. Faces the inscription <ref target="DHARMA_INSPallava00064"/> which has almost exactly the same content.</p>
